# Message API Tests

### Create a new message
POST {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME_MESSAGE"
}

###

### Get message by ID (use the ID from the created message)
GET {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get message by code
GET {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message/code/WELCOME_MESSAGE
Accept: application/json

###

### Add localized text for the message (replace messageId with actual ID)
POST {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message/1/localized
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "languageId": 1,
  "text": "Welcome to our application!"
}

###

### Add Arabic localized text for the message (replace messageId with actual ID)
POST {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message/1/localized
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "languageId": 2,
  "text": "مرحبا بكم في تطبيقنا!"
}

###

### Get localized message (English)
GET {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message/localized/WELCOME_MESSAGE?languageId=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get localized message (Arabic)
GET {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message/localized/WELCOME_MESSAGE?languageId=2
Accept: application/json

###

### Get paginated messages
GET {{Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/message?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

